title: Ep - 39 - Jessica Evans of Laguna Beach & Cortney Hendrix from Married at First Sight
description:
Jessica Smith Evans from MTV's Laguna Beach talks about the impact of being filmed for a tv show while in high school and whether she keeps in touch with cast mates. Cortney Hendrix from Married at First Sight explains how she is still happily married to a stranger she met on television. Kate forces her sister Megan to watch an episode of Return to Amish.
